  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a full kettle</p><p>Peel and grate <strong>half</strong> your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Slice the<strong> remaining onion </strong>finely</p><p>Slice your <strong>chestnut mushrooms</strong></p><p>Slice <strong>half</strong> your <strong>red chilli[es]</strong> into rounds and finely dice the <strong>remaining red chilli</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1697643269291-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1697643269291-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1697643269291-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1697643269291-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1697643269291-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>grated onion</strong>, <strong>diced chilli </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)<strong> </strong>and<strong> pork mince </strong>(remove the paper if required!) with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Divide the <strong>meatball mixture</strong> and shape them into 4 meatballs per person</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1697643277201-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1697643277201-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1697643277201-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1697643277201-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1697643277201-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium-high heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>meatballs</strong> to the pan and cook for 2 min on each side or until browned</p><p>Once the <strong>meatballs</strong> have browned, transfer them to a plate and set aside, these will finish cooking in the sauce later (reserve the pan!)</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
