    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>rice noodles</strong> to a pot and cover them with <strong>boiled water</strong> until fully submerged</p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 3-4 min or until tender, then drain</p><p>Once drained, return the <strong>noodles</strong> to the pot and set aside</p>",
