          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a medium-high heat, with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced onion </strong>and <strong>sliced mushrooms </strong>and cook for 3-4 min or until softened</p><p>Once softened, add your <strong>pho broth paste</strong>, <strong>toasted sesame oil</strong>, <strong>ginger & garlic paste </strong>and <strong>soy sauce </strong>with 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[300ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [400ml]<strong> </span>boiled water</strong></p>",
