    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>pork meatball & mushroom pho</strong></p><p>Garnish with the<strong> sliced spring onion</strong>, <strong>chilli rounds </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)<strong> </strong>and <strong>chopped mint & coriander</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
